      <title>随着中国国会开幕，亚洲股市面临压力：市场结束</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-04/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</link>
      <description><![CDATA[亚洲股市周二普遍走低，投资者关注中国，中国官员公布了雄心勃勃的今年 5% 的增长目标，并采取了提振信心的措施。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-04/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 04 Mar 2024 23:14:14 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>澳大利亚小麦产量有望因天气好转而攀升</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-04/australia-s-wheat-production-slightly-higher-but-quality-mixed</link>
      <description><![CDATA[澳大利亚下个季节的小麦产量预计将增加，因为在经历了包括大雨和闷热在内的极端天气之后，天气好转改善了播种条件。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-04/australia-s-wheat-production-slightly-higher-but-quality-mixed</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 04 Mar 2024 13:01:00 GMT</pubDate>
